---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<Layout title="HCI Portfolio | Evaluation">
    <PageHeader 
        title="Evaluation & Refinement" 
        description="Testing our prototypes with users, gathering feedback, and refining the experience."
    />

    <Section title="User Testing Sessions">
        <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none mb-8">
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                We conducted usability testing sessions to validate our design decisions and identify areas for improvement.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Placeholder for testing methodology and setup -->
        <div class="bg-bg-darker border border-border-dark p-6 mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 font-display text-white">Testing Methodology</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-neutral-400 space-y-2">
                <li>(Number of participants)</li>
                <li>(Testing format: e.g., remote, moderated)</li>
                <li>(Key tasks tested)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </Section>

    <Section title="Key Findings & Refinements" class="bg-bg-darker/30 border-y border-border-dark">
        <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none mb-12">
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                Based on the feedback gathered, we iteratively improved the prototype. Here are the major changes we made.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-12">
            <!-- Refinement Item 1 -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
                <div class="bg-bg-dark border border-border-dark p-6">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-accent mb-2">Issue Identified</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm mb-4">(Describe what users struggled with)</p>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">Our Solution</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">(Describe how the design was changed to fix it)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="aspect-video bg-bg-darker border border-border-dark flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-10"></div>
                    <span class="font-mono text-neutral-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">BEFORE_AFTER.img</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Refinement Item 2 Placeholder -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
                <div class="bg-bg-dark border border-border-dark p-6">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-accent mb-2">Issue Identified</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm mb-4">(Describe what users struggled with)</p>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">Our Solution</h4>
                    <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">(Describe how the design was changed to fix it)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="aspect-video bg-bg-darker border border-border-dark flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-10"></div>
                    <span class="font-mono text-neutral-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">BEFORE_AFTER.img</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Section>
</Layout>